# About Me

Cardiology fellow with an interest in autonomic dysfunction, heart rate variability, epidemiology, biostatistics, and point-of-care ultrasonography.

# Education

```{r education}
entries %>%
	filter(section == "education") %>%
	arrange(start) %>%
	detailed_entries(
		when = glue("{start}--{end}"),
		what = title,
		where = location,
		with = institution,
		why = description
	) 
```

